{"tid":2209601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"標普：美對港銀行實施嚴厲制裁可能性非常低","createTime":"2020-09-19T18:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T03:33:09.000Z","uid":91914,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9250a8d2885f0fe7bd710b0d1f8f9a7ce1b3e632","tid":2209601,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:06:30.000Z","msg":"評級機構標普表示，美國對香港金融機構實施嚴厲制裁的可能性非常低，若果施加制裁的影響將會很大，但如果中美之間的緊張局勢升級，不確定性將會增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標普稱，其對香港銀行業的評估為世界上最強的之一，這主要得益於香港銀行的穩固資本和流動性緩衝，以及香港特區審慎有效的銀行法規，強大的支付文化，以及作為通往中國的重要門戶的獨特地位。"},{"pid":"d9f1e0eb844f6d84297d3fcd0c166ba76f242316","tid":2209601,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:07:45.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c1e8794d2b6ba5289f546c5ac1c8874cacdee8","tid":2209601,"uid":200663,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:07:49.000Z","msg":"被列入不可靠名單的 HSBC : <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34400b3dffb288dc820095281c1be3dbde49466","tid":2209601,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:10:57.000Z","msg":"因為勝利11人已經成為崑崙銀行尊貴客戶，其他銀行已經割𥱊"},{"pid":"8500148c47fb8a72a7f01a53da4a402dc8477dae","tid":2209601,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T19:53:44.000Z","msg":"早幾年咪又話中美無可能脫勾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da8464fad594cd28cfb7f5a4e44891dd5f515d1","tid":2209601,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T20:23:01.000Z","msg":"可以先搞四大行香港分行先<br />\n唔一定要玩晒全部"},{"pid":"27d1baea6df3e1ca4593afe47cabe8209c100794","tid":2209601,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T01:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.g